data.description:
What a great house and for under 200K!! Located in the village of Carthage, walking distance to many shops and eateries. 
This cute house has a sweet front porch that opens into the large kitchen. Off the kitchen is a super nice laundry area and terrific butlers pantry.
Off the kitchen is a formal dining area, cozy living room and full bathroom.
Upstairs is a huge primary bedroom, 2 more decent sized bedrooms and another full bathroom.
The backyard is huge with the most beautiful hydrangea tree you will ever see! 
Check this one out quick and make it your new home today!
